title: A Real-Time Counseling Session with Dr. Alison Cook
description:
This is part 2 of our 3-part interview series with Dr. Alison Cook. Dr. Cook is a psychologist who has helped women, ministry leaders, couples, and families learn how to heal painful emotions, forge healthy relationships, and fully live out their God-given potential. Listen as she and Jennie dive into past hurts in a real-time counseling session.

Part 1 of this interview series: https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/made-for-this-with-jennie-allen/id1466667116?i=1000582501565
